text: Jönssonligan största kupp (English: The Jönsson Gang's Greatest Robbery) is a Swedish film about the gang Jönssonligan, released to cinemas in Sweden on 3 February 1995. ==Cast== *Stellan Skarsgård - Herman Melvin *Ulf Brunnberg - Vanheden *Björn Gustafson - Dynamit-Harry *Peter Haber - Doktor Busé *Birgitta Andersson - Doris *Per Grundén - Wall- Enberg *Weiron Holmberg - Johansson "Biffen" *Bernt Lindkvist - Egon Holmberg *Carl Magnus Dellow - Anton Beckman *Pontus Gustafsson - Konrad Andersson *Gösta Bredefeldt - Josef Burak *Elias Ringquist - Lillis *Lars-Göran Persson - Maffialeader *Maciej Koslowski - Ritzie *Jan Mybrand - Safety guard *Michael Segerström - Safety boss *Yvonne Schaloske - Hotel cleaner == External links == * * Category:Jönssonligan films Category:1995 films Category:Swedish comedy films Category:Films set in Warsaw Category:Swedish films
